{"tid":1758763,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"立法會選舉的最終幻想","createTime":"2019-11-27T09:09:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T10:23:35.000Z","uid":19648,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"13d951bf91270d83e45c2eeaff691d828997107d","tid":1758763,"uid":19648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:09:46.000Z","msg":"是次2019是以比例代表名單投票制<br />\n即是 一個名單第一名當選後的剩餘票會依次序分配分下一順位 用最大餘額法 計算名單第二名能不能當選 如此類推<br />\n<br />\n而為備戰立法會<br />\n<br />\n本人建議泛民本土及港獨派統籌單一組合名單以應付中共的強大配票機制及泛民歷年名單協調失敗導致贏票數輸議席<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;名單組成辦法&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n是以十八區區議會勝利的基礎，舉行十八區名單初選，以各區議員的辦工室為民調及票務收集中心，進行實名登記的民調初選。而投票模式應為多票制，令組成名單排序有更高的公信力。<br />\n<br />\n而初選名單可以為提名制， 以現任立法會議員或區議會議為提名人。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;宣傳&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n為迎合港豬口味，其行動名建議為最後的名單，吸引各界眼球。<br />\n<br />\n利用十八區初選機制， 增加立法會投票資訊在十八區曝光率，增加投入感和投票率。 <br />\n<br />\n&mdash;未完&mdash;<br />\n請提供意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e997f6f3156fbf489db6e47215f763561de275","tid":1758763,"uid":241979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:10:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a7b146e8ac178592dfb9e58b32d04230c4445c8","tid":1758763,"uid":178115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:12:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"976ec2fdaf5bccf623203f9876dcdbbbdbff708b","tid":1758763,"uid":19648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a7b146e8ac178592dfb9e58b32d04230c4445c8","tid":1758763,"uid":178115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:12:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:15:11.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"8d16bff7281b3d2addc56dede6e40e70c33d8147","tid":175